Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:02.55,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}de uma nova forma,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:07.02,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Vou colocar todos meus sentimentos,
